msgctxt "1248_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"The prices are reasonable and the food is pretty yummy. And\r\n"
"with their twentieth anniversary, all the restaurants\r\n"
"underwent a huge remodel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1260_Haruka"
msgid "Hmm. I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1272_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"And then there's Watamin-chi, the charcoal grill restaurant.\r\n"
"They're about ten years younger than Watami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1284_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"They focus on charcoal-grilled foods and stews. Their food\r\n"
"is well-priced and yummy, too!"
msgstr ""

