"He said it was so much fun seeing the singers he loved get\r\n"
"popular that he finally just decided to get into the\r\n"
"business officially."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2232_Haruka"
msgid "Wow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2244_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"Once he got into the industry, he said it was time to grow\r\n"
"up and put aside his groupie ways."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2256_Haruka"
msgid "Hehe. He's very dedicated, isn't he?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2268_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"But even now, he still goes to see his favorites' concerts\r\n"
"on his days off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2280_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"Apparently, he went to see an idol named Airi Yuki perform\r\n"
"recently, and somebody from another agency caught him tons\r\n"
"of souvenirs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2292_Haruka"
msgid ""
"Hehe! I bet he'll never live that one down. It sure sounds like he loves "
"idols!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2304_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"Hey, here's a thought! I bet Horie-kun'd love to get Airi\r\n"
"Yuki's autograph, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2316_Haruka"
msgid "Ah, that's a great idea!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2328_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"That settles it, then! Haruka, I want ya to go see Airi Yuki\r\n"
"and get her autograph for Horie-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2340_Haruka"
msgid ""
"You mean right now!? But isn't it kind of awkward to try\r\n"
"seeing her without making an appointment first or anything?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2352_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"But that's the kind of thing Horie-kun did for you every\r\n"
"single day to get you work. It's what we in the business\r\n"
"call \"walk-in sales.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2364_Haruka"
msgid "Well, when you put it that way... All right, I'll do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2376_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"Good girl! Oh, hold on. At least lemme help ya find out\r\n"
"where she's at right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2400_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"Hello. This is Misa Yamaura from Dyna Chair. Could you tell\r\n"
"me where Airi Yuki-san is scheduled to perform today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2412_Yamaura"
msgid "Ah, I see. Thank you very much. All right. Goodbye, now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2436_Haruka"
msgid "What did you find out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2448_Yamaura"
msgid ""
"This will work out great! She's gonna be performing at\r\n"
"Castle Records, they said. Go get that autograph!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2460_Haruka"
msgid ""
"(My goodness. Yamaura-san can be a little pushy sometimes...\r\n"
"But this is for Horie-san, and he's always doing so much for\r\n"
"me, so surely I can do this for him!)"
msgstr ""